About the game:

It's a girl! And a boy! In fact, it's every adorable baby in DinerTown, all bundled up for you to lavish with love, in Diaper Dash. Keep the DinerTown darlings cooing by helping out Wilson, who's in over his head running the local daycare. Now's the time to make a play-date with the game that's literally crawling with fun! Play 50 baby-filled levels and purchase over 20 upgrades, from stain-free walls to auto-rocking cradles. Meet the kids of your favorite DinerTown residents. Cute and cuddly was never as much fun as in Diaper Dash!
